Package: decisiontree
Type: Package
Title: Implement decision tree
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xinwei Wang
Maintainer: Xinwei Wang <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: Including six different functions which are information_entropy(),
    calculate_infor_gain(), find_best_split(), myrpart(), predict_point() and
    predict_dateset(). The first four functions are responsible for constructing
    a decision tree, while the last two functions are used to make predictions 
    using the trained tree model.
